column4: what is the associated musical artist of <A>
In how many languages did <A> sing?
column5: SELECT DISTINCT COUNT(?uri) where { ?x dbp:artist <A> . ?x dbp:language ?uri }

column4: <A> did the music for what movies?
column5: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri where { ?uri dbp:music <A> . ?uri a dbo:Film }
column6: select distinct ?a where { ?uri dbp:music ?a . ?uri a dbo:Film }

column4: <A> has composed music for how many things?
<A> is a musical instrument played by which artists?
column5: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri where { ?uri dbo:instrument <A> . ?uri a dbo:MusicalArtist }
column6: select distinct ?a where { ?uri dbo:instrument ?a . ?uri a dbo:MusicalArtist }

column4: <A> is the member of what band?
column5: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri where { ?uri dbp:currentMembers <A> . ?uri a dbo:Band }
column6: select distinct ?a where { ?uri dbp:currentMembers ?a . ?uri a dbo:Band }

column4: For which band did <A> perform in the past?
What are some famous artists who rocked <A>?
column5: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri where { ?uri dbp:notableInstruments <A> . ?uri a dbo:MusicalArtist }
column6: select distinct ?a where { ?uri dbp:notableInstruments ?a . ?uri a dbo:MusicalArtist }

column4: What are the movies whose music is composed by <A>?
column5: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri where { ?uri dbo:musicComposer <A> . ?uri a dbo:Film }
column6: select distinct ?a where { ?uri dbo:musicComposer ?a . ?uri a dbo:Film }
